data.description: Welcome to Usher Drive! This home will have you saying "yeah, yeah". This 4 bed/3 bath home is spacious, updated, and perfect for entertaining. With over 3400 sq. ft, this home has hardwood floors, custom cabinetry, and granite countertops throughout. The large 8 x 5 island can seat 6 and is a showstopper. The breakfast nook leads you out to the 42 by 12 new composite deck that stretches the length of the home. The primary suite has a walk in closet, large bath with granite vanity and tile floor. The other two bedrooms have large closets and a shared bath. The staircase has been updated leading to the basement featuring a large family room, full bath, 4th bedroom, wet bar, and game room/office. Just outside the walkout basement is a large backyard with a vinyl fence. There is a two car garage that leads you to the mudroom/ laundry room. The driveway has been extended for additional parking. Parks, shopping, restaurants, SAFB, interstate access are all in close proximity. Assumable loan
